4mv0.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01r4mv0\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">Arts &amp; Culture</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Discover art by Wilkinson and Wadsworth at Your Paintings</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><span class=\"type\">See more at</span><span class=\"name\">bbc.co.uk/yourpaintings</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-3 gel\"><a href=\"http://camoupedia.blogspot.co.uk/\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01r48yc.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01r48yc\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-link\">Visit</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Learn more about art and camouflage at Camoupedia</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><span class=\"type\">Research blog by</span><span class=\"name\">Prof. Roy R Behrens</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-4 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01p32w3\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01snqzk.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01snqzk\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">U-boats, bombardment and coastal defence</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-5 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.camolab.com/index.php\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01r50k1.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01r50k1\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-link\">Visit</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">Science</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Explore more camouflage research from Bristol University</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><span class=\"type\">University of Bristol</span><span class=\"name\">Camo Lab</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-6 iwonder\n                    k-colour-palette-palette-4\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/z38rq6f\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp square\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x256/p01l3r7h.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01l3r7h\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">Has poetry distorted our view of World War One?</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/80x80/p01lj3z7.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Presented by</span><span class=\"name\">Ian McMillan</span></p></div></a></div></div></div></div></section><footer class=\"k-g-footer\"><div id=\"k-g-gn-footer\"><ol class=\"k-g-gn\"><li><a href=\"#zp3wpv4\">Wilkinson's dazzling idea</a></li><li><a href=\"#zyc2yrd\">The art of confusion</a></li><li><a href=\"#z8x3wmn\">Painting the fleet</a></li><li><a href=\"#zqpc2hv\">The man behind the brush</a></li><li><a href=\"#z2s9xnb\">A colourful impact</a></li><li><a href=\"#zxy8tfr\">The legacy of dazzle</a></li><li><a href=\"#zt3wpv4\">Did dazzle really make a difference?</a></li><li><a href=\"#z3k6b9q\">Where next?</a></li></ol></div><div class=\"k-g-lp\"><div class=\"k-g-lp-options\"><span>Languages:</span><a href=\"/guides/language/cy/zty8tfr\">Cymraeg</a><a href=\"/guides/language/gd/zty8tfr\">Gàidhlig</a><a href=\"/guides/language/ga/zty8tfr\">Gaeilge</a></div></div></footer></div>\n\n  </div>       </div> <div id=\"orb-footer\"  class=\"orb-footer orb-footer-grey\" > <aside role=\"complementary\"> 